:authenticated:

- create vite
  ? list of users
  ? list of groups
  + vite data

  -> success
     + vite id
  -> fail

- list all vites
  -> success
     + list of active vite ids

- get all vites
  -> success
     + list of active vites

- get vites
  + list of vite ids
  
  -> success
     + list of vites for given vite ids

- update vite
  + vite id
  + vite data

  -> success
  -> fail

- add vite users
  + vite id
  + list of users

  -> success
  -> fail

- remove vite user
  + vite id
  + list of users

  -> success
  -> fail

- add vite groups
  + vite id
  + list of groups

  -> success
  -> fail

- remove vite group
  + vite id
  + list of groups

  -> success
  -> fail

- accept vite
  + vite id

  -> success
  -> fail

- decline vite
  + vite id
  
  -> success
  -> fail

- send vite message
  + vite id
  + message

  -> success
  -> fail

- get vite update version
  -> success
     + update version 

- get all vite updates
  + vite id

  -> success
     + list of all vite updates

- get all vite updates after version
  + vite id
  + vite update version

  -> success
     + list of vite updates after update version
